# Import Files - Safe to Commit

✅ These files are safe to commit to Git:
- `import-to-nextcloud-deck.md` - Documentation
- `nextcloud-deck-import.json` - Import data (no credentials)
- `Willkommen bei Nextcloud Deck!.json` - Reference export
- `README.md` - This guide

❌ Do NOT add:
- Your own exports with personal data
- Modified configs with credentials
